Class ElementChemical

  • java.lang.Object

  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Argon, Carbon, Chlorine, Copper, Fluorine, Helium, Hydrogen, Iron, Nitrogen, Oxygen, Silver, Sodium, Sulfur, Tin, Tungsten

    public class ElementChemical
extends Element
    Abstract structure for a class defining one of the chemical elements. Subclasses are (or will be) defined to correspond to each element in the periodic table.
